  <brief_title>Intrapulmonary Percussive Ventilation for Children With Bronchiolitis on Non-Invasive Ventilation Support</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Controlled Study of the Use of Intrapulmonary Percussive Ventilation (IPV) for Children With Bronchiolitis Admitted to the Pediatric Intensive Care Unit (PICU) and Are on Non-Invasive Ventilation Support</official_title>
