  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective randomized study of patients admitted to the Pediatric Intensive Care Unit
      suffering from Bronchiolitis and are supported on Non Invasive Positive Pressure Ventilation.
      The patient population will be divided into two groups, one group will receive conventional
      treatment and the other group will receive conventional treatment and three times a day of
      physiotherapy using Intrapulmonary Percussive Ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
